SUMMARY:Taste of Improv - Improv Open Mic Georgetown Art Attack
DESCRIPTION:Whether you’re a student\, a pro\, or just checking out the Art Attack\, this is your chance to take the stage\, make bold choices\, and have a blast doing it.\n\nJoin Unexpected Productions Improv School as we join Georgetown’s ART ATTACK with a spontaneous showcase of improv talent. Bring your squad\, support each other\, and celebrate the joy of live\, unfiltered performance.\nHit the Georgetown Art Attack\, then head over to the Improv School.\nCome for the art. Stay for the improv. See you there!
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/taste-of-improv-improv-open-mic-georgetown-art-attack-2-2-2-2/2026-03-14/
LOCATION:Seattle Improv School\, 5700 6th Ave S\, Seattle\, WA\, 98101\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Taste-of-Improv-header.png
END:VEVENT
