SUMMARY:Seattle Suites: An Improvised Neil Simon Comedy
DESCRIPTION:Improvised comedy in the style of Neil Simon\, where one hotel suite becomes a comedic pressure cooker for 3 hilarious improvised tales\n\n\n\nOne hotel suite. Countless misunderstandings. Relentless laughs. \nSeattle Suite is a laugh-driven\, fully improvised play inspired by the style of Plaza Suite and California Suite\, capturing the signature humor of Neil Simon that is fast\, verbal\, and rooted in beautifully human flaws. Each night\, a single Seattle hotel room becomes the setting for interconnected scenes inspired by your suggestions\, friends overshare and spiral\, romantic gestures go wrong\, awkward silences stretch\, and small problems become big ones. The comedy comes from character and relationship\, building through sharp dialogue\, escalating tension\, and recognizable\, lived-in situations. Perfect for fans of smart comedy\, relationship humor\, and classic theatrical wit.
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/seattle-suites-an-improvised-neil-simon-comedy/2026-03-14/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike Place Market\, Seattle\, WA\, 98101\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Seattle-Suite_-Comedy-in-the-Clouds.png
END:VEVENT
