SUMMARY:700 Level Student Showcase
DESCRIPTION:Witness the creation of believable characters\, inspiring scenes\, and some improv magic by 700 level class.\n\n\n\nJoin the advanced students in our 700 class and witness them blossom with new improv skills. Under the guidance of our expert improv teachers\, 700 students are learning new narrative formats and enhancing their skills by working in an ensemble. You get to see the fruits of their efforts by witnessing the creation of believable characters\, inspiring scenes\, and some improv magic.
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/700-level-student-showcase-2/2026-03-18/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike Place Market\, Seattle\, WA\, 98101\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/700.jpg
END:VEVENT
