SUMMARY:IMPROV 100 WEDNESDAYS - Intro to Improv: Say Yes!\, SPRING'26
DESCRIPTION:You are registered. Welcome!\nThank you for registering for this eight-week course at Unexpected Productions Improv. We’re excited to have you join us. \nPlease read the details below carefully. This information is important.\nTime and Dates: Wednesdays for eight (8) weeks\, from March 25 to May 23\, 7pm to 9:30pm \nImportant Attendance Note\nAttendance at the first session is mandatory\, as it sets the agenda for the entire quarter.\nIf you think you may miss the first class\, we strongly recommend registering for the next quarter instead. \nLocation: 5700 6th Ave St\, Suite 109\, Umbrella Room\, Seattle\, WA 98108\nClass Details\n• Maximum Students: 16\n• Cost: $295\n• Age Requirement: 18+ \nCancellation Policy\nIf you must cancel before the first class\, we can offer credit toward the same level class next quarter.\nWe are unable to offer refunds. If you cancel after the first class\, we cannot issue credit for a future class and cannot offer refunds.\nIf you have questions before the first class\, please contact us at school@unexpectedproductions.org \nWe look forward to working with you and can’t wait to get started.\nImprov classes are physically active and often involve movement\, standing\, and high-energy exercises\, so staying hydrated is important. \nWe recommend the following:\n• Comfortable clothing that allows for easy movement\n• Comfortable shoes\, as you will likely be standing and moving for extended periods\n• A notebook and pen\, if you would like to take notes on techniques or exercises\n• A water bottle (some locations do not have water fountains)\n• A “Yes\, And” attitude. A willingness to participate\, take risks\, and be brave is the most important thing to bring
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/improv-100-wednesdays-intro-to-improv-say-yes-spring26/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions Improv School ISSAQUAH/EASTSIDE\, 1315 NW Mall Street\, Suite 4\, Issaquah\, WA\, 98108\, United States
CATEGORIES:Education
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/100-Wednesdays.jpg
GEO:47.5520122;-122.3251523
